l sparsity, and provides a stronger $\\ell_2/\\ell_1$\nguarantee. Our system applies to \"for all\" sparse signals, is robust against\nbounded perturbations in $u$ as well as perturbations on $\\bestsignal$ itself.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 21 Mar 2012 14:40:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 21 Jun 2012 15:26:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-06-22"}
